<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Re-deliver" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Re-deliver,</orth> 1) to give back: <cit><quote>remembrances that I have longed long to r.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.1.94" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 1, 94</bibl></cit>. In <bibl n="shak. mm 4.4.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 4, 6</bibl> F<hi rend="sub">1</hi> <emph>reliver,</emph> F<hi rend="sub">2. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.4.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 4, 6</bibl> 4</hi> <emph>deliver,</emph> M. Edd. <emph>redeliver.</emph><lb />2) to report: <cit><quote>shall I r. you e'en so?</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.186" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 186</bibl></cit> (Qq <emph>deliver,</emph> q. v.).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>